text.tspan: Life expectation age 15, by sex, United States
Life expectation at birth for those currently aged 15, by sex, for the United States. For example, in 1790, a 15 year old
male in the US could expect to live until the age of 60.
Source: OWID based on Hacker (2010) and the US Social Security Administration (2017)
